<html>
<body>
<p>Reports non-public methods referenced in the <code>factory-method</code> attributes of <strong>&lt;bean&gt;</strong> elements.</p>

<p><b>Example:</b></p>
<pre><code lang="java">
public class MyFactory {
  private static FooBean createBean() {...}
  }
}
</code></pre>
<pre><code lang="xml">
&lt;beans&gt;
  &lt;bean class="MyFactory" factory-method="createBean"/&gt;
  // reports "Factory method 'createBean' should be public"
&lt;/beans&gt;
</code></pre>
</body>
</html>